text: Pachyneuridae is a family of gnats, gall midges, and March flies in the order Diptera. There are at least four genera and about five described species in Pachyneuridae. ==Genera== * Cramptonomyia * Haruka * Pachyneura * Pergratospes ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * * * ==External links== * Category:Bibionomorpha Category:Nematocera families
